  <?dbhtml filename="libxcursor.html"?>

  <title>libxcursor-&libxcursor-version;</title>

  <sect2 role="package">
    <title>Introduction</title>

    <para>
      Xcursor is a simple library designed to help locate and load cursors for
      the X Window System.
    </para>

